Dr. Toast Live @ Kelly Kemp & Co Fundraiser
posted February 20, 2008

Friday, February 22, 2008 - Kelly Kemp & Company Dance is a San Francisco-based group that presents some really wonderful modern dance. I'm honored to be playing music at their fundraising event. Free admission, open bar, silent auction, and donations accepted. 8-10:30pm, Dance Ground Keriac, 1805 Divisadero @ Bush, San Francisco.
